Class WaypointManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.droidplanner.services.android.impl.core.drone.DroneVariable
      • org.droidplanner.services.android.impl.core.MAVLink.WaypointManager

  • public class WaypointManager
extends DroneVariable
    Class to manage the communication of waypoints to the MAV.

    Should be initialized with a MAVLink Object, so the manager can send messages via the MAV link. The function processMessage must be called with every new MAV Message.
